Enclosing class:
Server
private class Server.ClientConnectionManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable

There is a ClientConnectionManager object per client connection, and a thread per ClientConnectionManager (created by the ServerInstance object). It paces sending the symbols at that rate, as best it can.

The ClientConnectionManager terminates only when the client breaks the connection.
